this is counterstrike 16 the latest version of the original counterstrike the graphics are far inferior to the source version but the gameplay is considered better by most counterstrike veterans this has some maps not found in the source verison and has the riot shield which is not in the source version either the riot shield allows you to avoid bullets but you cannot have a primary weapon if you have it equiped so you can only use your sidearm this version also features a gamemode not available in the source version the gamemode is where you must protect a player controlling a vip while they make their way to the rescue vehicle if you want to see how different this is from the source version then go right ahead its only $500 on steam so you have nothing to lose
