 one of the best games fps games ever made counterstrike 16 left its mark on the fps genera the community  the once prospering community has now reduced the number of adepts simply because the time for counterstrike 1016 has passed by a little bit and more and more of the once players of counterstrike are attracted now to these new big fpss and they are right to do that because we need to move and and progress the graphics  not so astonishing if you put it against the today graphics we must remember that it is an old game the graphics we look at today for this game were some hits back in 2000 and personally i still enjoy the graphics a little because they are bringing that simplicity not an eye heavy graphics style the sounds  well for me i still love the sounds in this game the guns sound like proper powerfull weapons when you press the button to fire you really feel like you are engaging somebody and you really feel like you are wielding a firearm that could take someones life not like some of todays fpss where guns sound more like the pops of the popcorn put in your microwave so here counterstrike still takes the point from some of the new fpss  even with the fact thats counterstrikes 16 time passed by a little bit i still recommend it and me too i still come back to it from time to time to enjoy this nice simple and clean graphics style the still impressive gun sounds and sometimes just to see where have we started from and where have we come with the fps genera note this is a personal opinnion you may agree or disagree with it but on whatever side you are you can leave a nice criticising comment instead of some hateful messages thank you
